    "Finally, in 2023 observed that the number of studies decreased to 37 articles.",
    "Within the scope of this inquiry, author-generated keywords constituted the primary analytical element and an examination of co-occurrence was undertaken.",
    "Keywords were included in the analysis based on a threshold of at least five mentions, leading to the identification of 30 distinct keywords.",
    "Notably, \"geogebra\" surfaced as the most prevalent keyword, registering 183 occurrences.",
    "Additional keywords that were frequently cited included \"dynamic geometry environment\" (frequency = 31), \"geometry\" (frequency = 26), and \"mathematics education\"/\"teaching\" (frequency = 24)."
